<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="rtl" lang="ar">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>خطة العمل - {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Arabic:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans Arabic', 'IBM Plex Sans Arabic', 'Tajawal', 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #2c2c2c;
            direction: rtl;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 21cm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2cm;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2E7D32;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -3px;
            right: 50%;
            transform: translateX(50%);
            width: 100px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1976D2, #2E7D32);
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2E7D32, #1976D2);
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .document-title {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2E7D32;
            margin: 20px 0 15px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .company-name {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1976D2;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #666;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .date-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #e3f2fd);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-right: 4px solid #2E7D32;
        }
        
        .hijri-date {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2E7D32;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .gregorian-date {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin: 50px 0;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2E7D32;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1f8e9, #e8f5e8);
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-right: 6px solid #2E7D32;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .section-title::before {
            content: counter(section-counter, arabic-indic);
            counter-increment: section-counter;
            position: absolute;
            right: -15px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #2E7D32;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        
        .subsection {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .subsection-title {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1976D2;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd, #f3e5f5);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-right: 4px solid #1976D2;
        }
        
        .content {
            line-height: 2;
            text-align: justify;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0, #fff8e1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-right: 4px solid #F57C00;
            margin: 25px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .highlight::before {
            content: "⭐";
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 20px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        
        .financial-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 0;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .financial-table th {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2E7D32, #388E3C);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        
        .financial-table td {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .financial-table tr:nth-child(even) td {
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .financial-table tr:hover td {
            background: #e8f5e8;
        }
        
        .amount {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2E7D32;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        
        .metric-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .metric-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #e3f2fd);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .metric-card:hover {
            border-color: #2E7D32;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.2);
        }
        
        .metric-value {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2E7D32;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .metric-label {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .timeline {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
            padding-right: 40px;
        }
        
        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            right: 15px;
            top: 10px;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            background: #2E7D32;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        
        .timeline-item::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px;
            top: 22px;
            width: 2px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #e0e0e0;
        }
        
        .timeline-item:last-child::after {
            display: none;
        }
        
        .timeline-content {
            flex: 1;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-right: 4px solid #2E7D32;
        }
        
        .timeline-date {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2E7D32;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        ul, ol {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-right: 30px;
        }
        
        li {
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .risk-matrix {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .risk-item {
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid;
        }
        
        .risk-high {
            background: #ffebee;
            border-color: #f44336;
            color: #d32f2f;
        }
        
        .risk-medium {
            background: #fff3e0;
            border-color: #ff9800;
            color: #f57c00;
        }
        
        .risk-low {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            border-color: #4caf50;
            color: #388e3c;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd, #f3e5f5);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding: 30px 0;
            border-top: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .arabic-number {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans Arabic', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        @media print {
            .container {
                box-shadow: none;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 1.5cm;
            }
            
            .section {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                page-break-after: avoid;
            }
        }
        
        body {
            counter-reset: section-counter;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                {{#if companyLogo}}
                    <img src="{{companyLogo}}" alt="{{companyName}}" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain;">
                {{else}}
                    برين سايت
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            <h1 class="document-title">خطة العمل</h1>
            <h2 class="company-name">{{companyName}}</h2>
            <p class="subtitle">خطة شاملة للأعمال في المملكة العربية السعودية</p>
            
            <div class="date-section">
                <div class="hijri-date">{{hijriDate}}</div>
                <div class="gregorian-date">الموافق {{gregorianDate}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Executive Summary -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">الملخص التنفيذي</h2>
            <div class="content">
                <p>{{executiveSummary}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <h3>الهدف الرئيسي</h3>
                <p>{{mainObjective}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="metric-grid">
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{investmentAmount}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">رأس المال المطلوب (ريال)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{expectedROI}}%</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">العائد المتوقع على الاستثمار</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{timeframe}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-label">المدة الزمنية (سنوات)</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Company Overview -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">نظرة عامة على الشركة</h2>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">رؤية الشركة</h3>
                <div class="content">{{companyVision}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">رسالة الشركة</h3>
                <div class="content">{{companyMission}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">القيم الأساسية</h3>
                <div class="content">
                    <ul>
                        {{#each coreValues}}
                        <li>{{this}}</li>
                        {{/each}}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">المعلومات الأساسية</h3>
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <p><strong>رقم السجل التجاري:</strong> <span class="arabic-number">{{crNumber}}</span></p>
                    <p><strong>الرقم الضريبي:</strong> <span class="arabic-number">{{vatNumber}}</span></p>
                    <p><strong>العنوان الوطني:</strong> {{nationalAddress}}</p>
                    <p><strong>رقم الهاتف:</strong> <span class="arabic-number">{{phoneNumber}}</span></p>
                    <p><strong>البريد الإلكتروني:</strong> {{email}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Products and Services -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">المنتجات والخدمات</h2>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">الخدمات الأساسية</h3>
                <div class="content">
                    {{#each services}}
                    <div class="highlight">
                        <h4>{{name}}</h4>
                        <p>{{description}}</p>
                        <p><strong>السعر المتوقع:</strong> <span class="amount arabic-number">{{price}} ريال</span></p>
                    </div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">الميزة التنافسية</h3>
                <div class="content">{{competitiveAdvantage}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Market Analysis -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">تحليل السوق</h2>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">السوق المستهدف</h3>
                <div class="content">{{targetMarket}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">حجم السوق</h3>
                <div class="metric-grid">
                    <div class="metric-card">
                        <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{marketSize}}</div>
                        <div class="metric-label">حجم السوق (مليون ريال)</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-card">
                        <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{marketGrowthRate}}%</div>
                        <div class="metric-label">معدل نمو السوق السنوي</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-card">
                        <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{marketShare}}%</div>
                        <div class="metric-label">الحصة السوقية المستهدفة</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">تحليل المنافسين</h3>
                <div class="content">
                    {{#each competitors}}
                    <div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <h4>{{name}}</h4>
                        <p><strong>نقاط القوة:</strong> {{strengths}}</p>
                        <p><strong>نقاط الضعف:</strong> {{weaknesses}}</p>
                        <p><strong>الحصة السوقية:</strong> <span class="arabic-number">{{marketShare}}%</span></p>
                    </div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Marketing Strategy -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">استراتيجية التسويق</h2>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">استراتيجية التسعير</h3>
                <div class="content">{{pricingStrategy}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">قنوات التوزيع</h3>
                <div class="content">
                    <ul>
                        {{#each distributionChannels}}
                        <li>{{this}}</li>
                        {{/each}}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">استراتيجية الترويج</h3>
                <div class="content">{{promotionStrategy}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Financial Projections -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">التوقعات المالية</h2>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">توقعات الإيرادات والمصروفات (بالريال السعودي)</h3>
                <table class="financial-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>البيان</th>
                            <th>السنة الأولى</th>
                            <th>السنة الثانية</th>
                            <th>السنة الثالثة</th>
                            <th>السنة الرابعة</th>
                            <th>السنة الخامسة</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>إجمالي الإيرادات</strong></td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year1.revenue}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year2.revenue}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year3.revenue}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year4.revenue}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year5.revenue}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>إجمالي المصروفات</strong></td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year1.expenses}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year2.expenses}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year3.expenses}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year4.expenses}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year5.expenses}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>صافي الربح</strong></td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year1.netProfit}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year2.netProfit}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year3.netProfit}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year4.netProfit}}</td>
                            <td class="amount arabic-number">{{financials.year5.netProfit}}</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">متطلبات التمويل</h3>
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="metric-grid">
                        <div class="metric-card">
                            <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{fundingRequirements.initialInvestment}}</div>
                            <div class="metric-label">الاستثمار الأولي (ريال)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="metric-card">
                            <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{fundingRequirements.workingCapital}}</div>
                            <div class="metric-label">رأس المال العامل (ريال)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="metric-card">
                            <div class="metric-value arabic-number">{{fundingRequirements.totalFunding}}</div>
                            <div class="metric-label">إجمالي التمويل المطلوب (ريال)</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Management Team -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">فريق الإدارة</h2>
            
            {{#each managementTeam}}
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">{{name}} - {{position}}</h3>
                <div class="content">
                    <p><strong>الخبرة:</strong> {{experience}}</p>
                    <p><strong>التعليم:</strong> {{education}}</p>
                    <p><strong>المسؤوليات:</strong> {{responsibilities}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>

        <!-- Implementation Timeline -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">الجدول الزمني للتنفيذ</h2>
            
            <div class="timeline">
                {{#each implementationPhases}}
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-date">{{date}}</div>
                        <h4>{{phase}}</h4>
                        <p>{{description}}</p>
                        <p><strong>المدة:</strong> {{duration}}</p>
                        <p><strong>التكلفة المتوقعة:</strong> <span class="amount arabic-number">{{cost}} ريال</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Risk Analysis -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">تحليل المخاطر</h2>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">مصفوفة المخاطر</h3>
                <div class="risk-matrix">
                    {{#each riskAnalysis}}
                    <div class="risk-item {{riskLevel}}">
                        <h4>{{riskType}}</h4>
                        <p>{{description}}</p>
                        <p><strong>التأثير:</strong> {{impact}}</p>
                        <p><strong>الاحتمالية:</strong> {{probability}}</p>
                        <p><strong>استراتيجية التخفيف:</strong> {{mitigationStrategy}}</p>
                    </div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Saudi Regulatory Compliance -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">الامتثال التنظيمي السعودي</h2>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">التراخيص المطلوبة</h3>
                <div class="content">
                    <ul>
                        {{#each requiredLicenses}}
                        <li>
                            <strong>{{name}}:</strong> {{description}}
                            <br><small>الجهة المصدرة: {{issuingAuthority}} | المدة: {{duration}}</small>
                        </li>
                        {{/each}}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">متطلبات الامتثال</h3>
                <div class="content">
                    <ul>
                        {{#each complianceRequirements}}
                        <li>{{this}}</li>
                        {{/each}}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Conclusion and Recommendations -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">الخلاصة والتوصيات</h2>
            
            <div class="content">
                <p>{{conclusion}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <h3>التوصيات الرئيسية</h3>
                <ul>
                    {{#each recommendations}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">الخطوات التالية</h3>
                <div class="timeline">
                    {{#each nextSteps}}
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <div class="timeline-date">{{timeline}}</div>
                            <h4>{{action}}</h4>
                            <p>{{details}}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>تم إعداد هذه الخطة بواسطة منصة برين سايت للتحول الرقمي</p>
            <p>للشركات الصغيرة والمتوسطة في قطاع الرعاية الصحية - المملكة العربية السعودية</p>
            <p class="arabic-number">{{currentDate}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>